      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "It takes to /explore/bengaluru or\n/explore/mumbai or /explore/delhi with\nrespect to the location of the user selected ,\non manualy changing the location the page\nloads according to selected location. if city\nis not selected the notification appears over\nscreen in red error which asks user to\nchoose city from above.",
      "fontSize": 68,
